---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../styles/services.css';
---

<Layout title="Accounting Services - ClimbHQ" description="Accounting services for climbing centres - bookkeeping, KPI dashboards and CFO support from £500/month. No jargon, just clear numbers." bodyClass="page-accounting">

<section class="service-hero" style="background-image: linear-gradient(200deg, rgba(7, 31, 51, 0.7) 20%, rgba(47, 36, 27, 0.6) 80%), url('/images/bg/woman-climbing-indoor.jpg'); background-position: center 50%;">
  <div class="service-hero-inner">
    <h1>Accounting Services</h1>
    <p>Our expert team of finance gurus use the latest systems and technology to make sure your finances are as safe as your climbing wall.</p>
    <p>In our Ascend and Apex packages you get dedicated personal support from our Finance Business Partners and CFOs making sure you get the insight you need to grow in the most profitable way.</p>
    <p>No Jargon, just easy to understand numbers that make sense and allow you to make the right decisions.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="pricing-section">
  <div class="pricing-grid pricing-grid-4">
    <div class="pricing-card">
      <h2>Anchor</h2>
      <p class="pricing-amount">FROM £500 per month</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Managing all your book-keeping needs</li>
        <li>Expense Tracking</li>
        <li>Analysing income</li>
        <li>Monthly pre-built financial reports</li>
        <li>Payroll</li>
        <li>Access to Customer Support</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="pricing-card featured">
      <h2>Ascend</h2>
      <p class="pricing-amount">FROM £1000 per month</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Everything in Anchor plus:</li>
        <li>More in-depth financial reports and KPI Dashboards</li>
        <li>Integrated KPI reporting including memberships &amp; attendance stats*</li>
        <li>Monthly dedicated Finance Business Partner check-in</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="pricing-card">
      <h2>Apex</h2>
      <p class="pricing-amount">FROM £1500 per month</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Everything in Ascend plus:</li>
        <li>Annual financial business planning including forecast creation and monthly performance measurement</li>
        <li>Bespoke financial reporting and dashboards</li>
        <li>Cashflow forecasting</li>
        <li>Half-day per month access to CFO for financial mentoring &amp; strategic advice</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="pricing-card">
      <h2>Add-ons</h2>
      <p class="pricing-amount">&nbsp;</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Support to raise finance / loans</li>
        <li>Event preparation e.g. sale / investment</li>
        <li>Support with acquisitions</li>
        <li>Accounting system migration</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p class="pricing-footnote">* Data permitting</p>
</section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .pricing-grid-4 {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr) !important;
  }
  .pricing-footnote {
    text-align: center;
    color: #9796A3;
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    margin-top: 24px;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .pricing-grid-4 {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr) !important;
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .pricing-grid-4 {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr !important;
    }
  }
</style>
